<li id="cite_note-Yuji1-11"><b><a href="#cite_ref-Yuji1_11-0" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal">Ukai, Yuji; Soeder, Derek; Permeh, Ryan (2004). "<a href="http://www.blackhat.com/presentations/bh-asia-04/bh-jp-04-ukai-eng.ppt" class="external text" title="http://www.blackhat.com/presentations/bh-asia-04/bh-jp-04-ukai-eng.ppt" rel="nofollow">Environment Dependencies in Windows Exploitation</a>". <i>BlackHat Japan</i>, Japan: eEye Digital Security.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=proceeding&amp;rft.btitle=BlackHat+Japan&amp;rft.atitle=Environment+Dependencies+in+Windows+Exploitation&amp;rft.aulast=Ukai&amp;rft.aufirst=Yuji&amp;rft.date=2004&amp;rft.pub=eEye+Digital+Security&amp;rft.place=Japan&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.blackhat.com%2Fpresentations%2Fbh-asia-04%2Fbh-jp-04-ukai-eng.ppt"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
